<HEADLINE> French Defense Minister, Army Chief of Staff to Visit India </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, April 20 (Xinhua) -- French Defense Minister Alain
Richard and Chief of General Staff of the French Armed Forces,
General Jean-Pierre Kelche, will visit India in the coming weeks,
the French Defense Ministry announced on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
