<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 20 (Xinhua) -- Pianist Javier Rovira and
guitarist Rafael Serrallet, both from Spain, will hold separate
concerts Beijing's Century Theater on April 25 and May 9.
</P>
<P>
Performance organizers with Century Performance Corporation
said today that the two musicians will give Beijing audiences an
evening of unique Spanish sound.
</P>
<P>
Rovira studied at the Royal Conservatoire in Brussels under the
direction of two famous Russian pianists, Evgancy Aloguievsk and
Olga Roummechevith.
</P>
