Iberia, Polonesa Fantasia Op. 61 and Cuatro Mazurkas Op. 17.
</P>
<P>
Music critics call Serralet one of the most acclaimed
guitarists of his generation, saying that he has positioned
himself to be one of the world's great masters of classical guitar.
</P>
<P>
He has presented guitar recitals in several major venues around
the world, such as the Lincoln Center in New York City, Mozart
Music Hall in Sao Paulo, Brazil, and the National Gallery of
Ottawa in Canada.
</P>
<P>
