<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 20 (Xinhua) -- More than 800 auto manufacturers
from 22 countries and regions have expressed their willingness to
participate in the sixth Beijing International Auto Industry
Exposition to be held from June 6 to 12.
</P>
<P>
Twenty-three world famous auto-manufacturers such as Mercedes
Benz, BMW, Volkswagen, Audi, General Motors, Ford, Citroen, Toyota,
Honda and Volvo have applied for exhibition, according to a report
in the latest issue of Beijing Review.
</P>
<P>
