international seminar on the global and Chinese auto industry in
the 21st century, an auto photograph competition, a national
competition of auto designs by youth and children and a national
competition of auto paintings by children, will be staged to add
cultural charm to the industrial exhibition.
</P>
<P>
Chinese enterprises, including Shanghai-GM, Shanghai Volkswagen,
FAW, Guangzhou Hongda, Citreon-Fukang and other complete
automobile manufacturers from Shenyang and Fujian are also to be
present at the exposition.  
