</P>
<P>
-- Africa at present has about 3.3 million refugees but to this
number should be added more than 15 million internally displaced
people, said regional director for southern Africa of the United
Nations High Commissioner for Refugees Nicolas Bwakira in Pretoria
on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Business Day:
</P>
<P>
-- The Johannesburg Stock Exchange has proposed sweeping
changes to its listing requirements designed to bolster investor
confidence in South Africa's equity market. 
