<DOCNO> XIE20000420.0277 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-20 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Results from WTA Tournament in Hilton Head </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, April 19 (Xinhua) -- Following are the results on
Wednesday at the Hilton Head Island women's tennis tournament in
South Carolina (prefix number denotes seeding):
</P>
<P>
Second round
</P>
<P>
1-Mary Pierce, France, beat Gala Leon Garcia, Spain, 6-1, 6-1
</P>
<P>
2-Conchita Martinez, Spain, bt Magui Serna, Spain, 7-6 (9-7), 6-
1
</P>
<P>
4-Arantxa Sanchez Vicario, Spain, bt Paola Suarez, Argentina, 6-
3, 7-5
