<HEADLINE> Mexico Issues Bonds in Japan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MEXICO CITY, April 19 (Xinhua) -- The Mexican government has
issued 50 billion yen (480 million U.S. dollars) in bonds in Japan,
the Ministry of Treasury and Public Credit said Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
