<HEADLINE> South American Strategic intelligence Congress to be Held in Chile </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The representatives of the armies of the American countries
will meet in Vina del Mar to discuss the issues of strategic
intelligence.
</P>
<P>
The multilateral military meeting will be attended by
specialists from Argentina, Bolivia, Colombia, Chile, Ecuador, the
United States, Paraguay, Uruguay and Venezuela.
</P>
<P>
The meeting aims to promote the development of a new concept of
subregional strategic intelligence through cooperation and
integration and assume the new challenges at the start of a new
millennium. 
</P>
